summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Southern Pacific Addition to West Seattle; the Northeast quarter of Section 16, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; the Southeast Quarter of Section 18, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, Supplement to J.J.
